TestMethod.Description: A client MAY select one or more GREASE named group values and advertise them in the "supported_groups" extension, if sent.  It MAY also send KeyShareEntry values for a subset of those selected in the "key_share" extension.  For each of these, the "key_exchange" field MAY be any value. [...]Servers MUST NOT negotiate any GREASE value when offered in a ClientHello. Servers MUST correctly ignore unknown values in a ClientHello and attempt to negotiate with one of the remaining parameters.
